Class Evaluator

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.uzh.agglorecommender.recommender.Evaluator

  • public class Evaluator
extends java.lang.Object
    Instantiates a new evaluation builder Evaluation builder offers evaluation methods (single,multiple) to calculate rmse It also offers helper methods to pick test users randomly from test set or create random users as input nodes for recommendations
